## Brightness control
XF86MonBrightness{Down,Up}
	backlight_control.sh {-5, +5}
mod5 + {End, Next}
	backlight_control.sh {-10, +10}
XF86Launch1
	backlight_toggle.sh

## Ctrl_R as mouse button 3
{Control_R, Shift_R}
	xte {'mouseclick 3', 'mouseclick 2'}

## Redlight
mod5 + {Prior, Home}
	redshift {-x, -O 3000}	

## Sound control
XF86Audio{Mute,LowerVolume,RaiseVolume}
	amixer sset Master {0%, 5%-, 5%+}

## Ending Session
XF86Launch2
	shut_reb.sh

## Print
Print
	print.sh

## Terminal
super + shift + Return
	st

## HTOP
super + shift + h
	st htop

